* &#x27;Cairo-Haifa Train Mined Again 40 Killed And 60 Wounded, Problem Of Preserving Sanctity Of Jerusalem&#x27;, &quot;The Times&quot;, Thursday, April 1, 1948; pg. 4; Issue 51034; col A.
